OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMartin Lewis says he was   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frejected by House of Lords 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Consumer champion Martin Lewis has     
OL,6, revealed that he applied recently to   
OL,7, become a member of the House of Lords  
OL,8, but was turned down.                   
OL,10,FThe founder of the Money Saving Expert 
OL,11,Fwebsite told the BBC's Nick Robinson he
OL,12,Fhad been "honest" about not having     
OL,13,Fenough time to attend many sittings.   
OL,15,FHe added that his "most important job" 
OL,16,Fwas looking after his nine-year-old    
OL,17,Fdaughter during early evenings.        
OL,19,FMr Lewis said he would be more ready   
OL,20,Ffor politics in a couple of years.     
